==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun|head=[[simple]] [[past]]}}

# {{context|grammar|lang=en}} A [[tense]] used to describe something that happened in the past, formed by inflection of a single word (i.e., without any auxiliary verb such as ''be'' or ''have'').

